  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to the National Episcopal Conference of Congo in communication material</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The world is currently going through a dramatic moment due to the Covid 19 pandemic. It is since March 10 that this pandemic has been declared in DRC, specifically in Kinshasa. Two weeks later, there were border closures and stopping of flights to the various provinces. Until now, the mobility of people from one province to another is still prohibited and means of transport are not yet authorized to circulate from one province to another. Even in the case of the reopening of these borders, the procedure will be in order for the movement of people in order to avoid a wide contagion, especially for people of an advanced age. With the restrictions associated with covid-19, the Bishops are unable to meet face to face. It is for this reason that CENCO approached CAFOD to ask for its support. This project aims to support CENCO with some communication materials to facilitate them to communicate virtually by video conference.</narrative>
  </description>
